RE Draft ISDA Master AgreementsMarie FinallyIm getting back to you with comments on these ISDAs Although the counterparty is now proposing something different I thought I would send you this for your files Im attaching the document that I went through for Georgia Power The changes to the documents are the same for all three with exception of the specified thresholds The only difference will be the thresholds as follows Savannah Electric and Power Company rd Party debt for Party B changed to MM will be acceptable Threshold of MM will be acceptable and the minimum transfer amount should be M not as they requested Mississippi Power Company rd Party debt for Party B being changed to MM will be acceptable Threshold should be countered to MM and min transfer countered at M Georgia Power Company Threshold info etc is located in the attached document Ive highlighted all of my comments in yellow below Again the same comments except for the thresholds etc mentioned above should resemble the other two documents Please give me a call if you have any questions Thanks again and I apologize for the delay Veronica Original Message From Heard Marie Sent Friday July AM To Espinoza Veronica Tenaska Cc several outstanding issues currently with Tenaskathe most significant being their change in ownership They are no longer an affilitatesub of Illinova Corp As Illinova has been acquired by Dynegy but have now seperated into the entities Tenaska Energy Inc and Tenaska Energy Holdings their financials are combined The Guarantor is collectively both entities Im currently working on amending the Master Swap Agreement as the credit support provider has changed Preliminary revised thresholds are between MM ENA has not Macd the counterparty bc the Illinovas gty etc will remain acitve until April Nontheless we need to amend accordingly ASAP Our current Financial MTM is MM I will also contact the physical legal group to have a new contract issued out as we have an old Master Physical Gas contract On the physical side attached below is a breakdown of our positions Please note that we have formal gas netting agreements for the ENA business As you can see the majority of the exposure is with the Canadian sales to their Canadian affitliate Also note that all of this business is still gtyd by Illinova until April An important note here is that I received a gty from the new guarantors today in the amount of MM covering Enron Corp and all of its subs It covers the physical business of Tenaska Marketing Ventures Tenaska Marketing Canada a Division of TMV Corp and Tenaska Gas Storage LLC Tenaska is also doing business with EES Once the ISDA is amended the new financial gtys will be issued out accordingly Also Im working with Global Counterparty to change the system accordingly I will keep you all updated on any changesprogress Please let me know if Ive left anything out Veronica

Tenaska Cc several outstanding issues currently with Tenaskathe most significant being their change in ownership They are no longer an affilitatesub of Illinova Corp As Illinova has been acquired by Dynegy but have now seperated into the entities Tenaska Energy Inc and Tenaska Energy Holdings their financials are combined The Guarantor is collectively both entities Im currently working on amending the Master Swap Agreement as the credit support provider has changed Preliminary revised thresholds are between MM ENA has not Macd the counterparty bc the Illinovas gty etc will remain acitve until April Nontheless we need to amend accordingly ASAP Our current Financial MTM is MM I will also contact the physical legal group to have a new contract issued out as we have an old Master Physical Gas contract On the physical side attached below is a breakdown of our positions Please note that we have formal gas netting agreements for the ENA business As you can see the majority of the exposure is with the Canadian sales to their Canadian affitliate Also note that all of this business is still gtyd by Illinova until April An important note here is that I received a gty from the new guarantors today in the amount of MM covering Enron Corp and all of its subs It covers the physical business of Tenaska Marketing Ventures Tenaska Marketing Canada a Division of TMV Corp and Tenaska Gas Storage LLC Tenaska is also doing business with EES Once the ISDA is amended the new financial gtys will be issued out accordingly Also Im working with Global Counterparty to change the system accordingly I will keep you all updated on any changesprogress Please let me know if Ive left anything out Veronica
